---
layout: base.njk
permalink: /
title: "Revista Digital ChefBrico | Comida de Verdade"
description: "Receitas 100% naturais, prontas em 18 minutos. O método da Chef Maria Conceição para uma rotina saudável e sem desperdício."
image: "/imagens/maria-conceicao-empreendedora-feira-tematica.png"

# --- SCHEMA INTEGRAL PRESERVADO (NÃO MEXER) ---
schema: {
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@graph": [
    {
      "@type": "WebSite",
      "name": "ChefBrico Gourmet Prático",
      "url": "https://gourmetpratico.com.br"
    },
    {
      "@type": "Organization",
      "name": "ChefBrico",
      "logo": "https://gourmetpratico.com.br/imagens/logo.png"
    }
  ]
}
---

<style>
/* --- ENGENHARIA VISUAL APPLE (RESPIRO & MARGENS) --- */
:root {
    --apple-white: #FFFFFF;
    --apple-cream: #FDFBF7;
    --chef-green: #014039;
    --chef-orange: #F2811D;
    --respiro-lateral: 24px; /* Margem de segurança Apple */
}

.magazine-container { 
    background-color: var(--apple-white); 
    padding-bottom: 100px;
    overflow-x: hidden; /* Evita quebra de layout lateral */
}

/* 1. HERO EDITORIAL COM RESPIRO */
.hero-premium-editorial {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 60px;
    padding: 80px var(--respiro-lateral); 
    max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto;
}

.avatar-circle-protector {
    width: 240px; height: 240px; border-radius: 50% !important;
    overflow: hidden; flex-shrink: 0;
    border: 8px solid var(--apple-cream); 
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
}
.avatar-circle-protector img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; }

.editorial-title { color: var(--chef-green); font-family: 'Merriweather', serif; font-size: 2.8rem; line-height: 1.1; margin: 0; }
.editorial-subtitle { color: #555; font-size: 1.2rem; line-height: 1.6; margin-top: 20px; max-width: 600px; }

/* 2. ENGENHARIA DO CARROSSEL (FIM DOS CARDS GRUDADOS) */
.carousel-magazine-row { 
    margin: 60px 0; 
}

/* Títulos alinhados com a margem lateral */
.carousel-magazine-row h2 { 
    color: var(--chef-green); 
    font-size: 1.6rem; 
    margin-bottom: 25px; 
    padding: 0 var(--respiro-lateral); 
}

.magazine-carousel {
    display: flex; 
    overflow-x: auto; 
    gap: 20px;
    padding: 10px var(--respiro-lateral) 40px var(--respiro-lateral); /* Respiro interno para scroll */
    scroll-snap-type: x mandatory;
    scrollbar-width: none;
    -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
}
.magazine-carousel::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }

/* 3. CARDS PADRONIZADOS (16:10 + CREAM) */
.magazine-card {
    flex: 0 0 300px; 
    background: var(--apple-cream); 
    border-radius: 24px;
    overflow: hidden; 
    text-decoration: none;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
    transition: transform 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1); 
    scroll-snap-align: start;
    border: 1px solid rgba(1, 64, 57, 0.04);
}
.magazine-card:hover { transform: translateY(-10px); box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); }

.card-img-rect { width: 100%; aspect-ratio: 16 / 10; object-fit: cover; }

/* AJUSTES MOBILE FIRST */
@media (max-width: 768px) {
    :root { --respiro-lateral: 20px; }
    .hero-premium-editorial { 
        flex-direction: column; 
        text-align: center; 
        padding: 40px var(--respiro-lateral); 
        gap: 30px;
    }
    .avatar-circle-protector { width: 190px; height: 190px; }
    .editorial-title { font-size: 2.1rem; }
    .magazine-card { flex: 0 0 270px; }
}
</style>

<main class="magazine-container">
    <section class="hero-premium-editorial">
        <div class="avatar-circle-protector">
            <img src="/imagens/maria-conceicao-agrovillage-caminho-chefbrico.png" alt="Maria Conceição">
        </div>
        <div class="editorial-content">
            <span style="color: var(--chef-orange); font-weight: 800; font-size: 0.8rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 2px;">Inspirar & Cuidar</span>
            <h1 class="editorial-title">Comida de Verdade;<br><span style="font-weight: 300; color: #999;">Sem confusão na cozinha!</span></h1>
            <p class="editorial-subtitle">Uma revolução no sabor e na sua rotina. Refeições práticas, 100% naturais e com o afeto da nossa cozinha artesanal.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="carousel-magazine-row">
        <h2>Comece por Aqui: O Método</h2>
        <div class="magazine-carousel">
            {% for post in collections.metodo %}
            <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="magazine-card">
                <img src="{{ post.data.image }}" class="card-img-rect" alt="{{ post.data.title }}">
                <div style="padding: 24px;">
                    <span style="color: var(--chef-orange); font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 800; text-transform: uppercase;">{{ post.data.category }}</span>
                    <h3 style="color: var(--chef-green); margin: 10px 0; font-size: 1.15rem;">{{ post.data.title }}</h3>
                    <p style="color: #666; font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.5;">{{ post.data.description | truncate(80) }}</p>
                </div>
            </a>
            {% endfor %}
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="carousel-magazine-row">
        <h2>Tendências & Bem-Estar</h2>
        <div class="magazine-carousel">
            {% for post in collections.fragmentos | sort(attribute='data.order') %}
            <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="magazine-card" style="border-top: 4px solid var(--chef-orange);">
                <div style="padding: 25px;">
                    <span style="color: var(--chef-orange); font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 800; text-transform: uppercase;">Dica da Chef</span>
                    <h3 style="color: var(--chef-green); font-size: 1rem; margin: 10px 0;">{{ post.data.title }}</h3>
                    <p style="color: #666; font-size: 0.85rem; line-height: 1.6;">{{ post.data.description | truncate(110) }}</p>
                    <span style="display: block; margin-top: 15px; font-weight: bold; color: var(--chef-green); font-size: 0.8rem;">Ler na Revista ➝</span>
                </div>
            </a>
            {% endfor %}
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="carousel-magazine-row">
        <h2>Quatro Universos de Sabor</h2>
        <div class="magazine-carousel">
            <a href="/receitas/risotos/" class="magazine-card">
                <img src="/imagens/risoto-pomodori-pesto-chefbrico-580px.png" class="card-img-rect">
                <div style="padding: 22px;">
                    <h3 style="color: var(--chef-green);">Risotos e Arrozes</h3>
                    <p style="color: #666; font-size: 0.9rem;">O clássico em 18 minutos.</p>
                </div>
            </a>
            <a href="/receitas/sopas-funcionais/" class="magazine-card">
                <img src="/imagens/chefbrico-creme-fit-sopinha-chefbrico-580 px.png" class="card-img-rect">
                <div style="padding: 22px;">
                    <h3 style="color: var(--chef-green);">Sopas Funcionais</h3>
                    <p style="color: #666; font-size: 0.9rem;">Leveza para suas noites.</p>
                </div>
            </a>
            <a href="/receitas/refeicoes-integrais/" class="magazine-card">
                <img src="/imagens/refeicao-nutritiva-integral-arroz-negro-chefbrico-80 px.png" class="card-img-rect">
                <div style="padding: 22px;">
                    <h3 style="color: var(--chef-green);">Refeições Integrais</h3>
                    <p style="color: #666; font-size: 0.9rem;">Grãos nobres e saúde.</p>
                </div>
            </a>
            <a href="/receitas/emporio-da-chef/" class="magazine-card">
                <img src="/imagens/confitado-shiitake-chefbrico.png" class="card-img-rect">
                <div style="padding: 22px;">
                    <h3 style="color: var(--chef-green);">Empório da Chef</h3>
                    <p style="color: #666; font-size: 0.9rem;">Acessórios gourmet finais.</p>
                </div>
            </a>
        </div>
    </section>
</main>
